:: P01
<<nobr>>The attic holds its breath. Dust hisses at your outline like it recognizes a shape.<</nobr>>
<div class="dialogue">Heh. The room knows you. I smile like a cut. What are you tonight—forecast or fog?</div>
<<if visited("P01") > 1>>
<div class="dialogue">Back again on purpose? Echoes wear new shoes when you return. Don't scuff the floor.</div>
<</if>>

<<timedprogressbar $timer>>
  <<goto "P03">>
<</timedprogressbar>>

[[Stay|P02]]
<<if $anger > 10 or $stress > 20>>[[Flinch|P06]]<</if>>
[[Reach to steady him|P09]]


:: P02
<div class="dialogue">Terms then. You witness, you don't mend. Let the dust decide what counts tonight.</div>
<div class="dialogue">Blink if you must, but don't bless me with pity. It makes my ribs itch.</div>
<<if visited("P02") > 1>>
<div class="dialogue">You know the pact by now. Quiet is a vote you can't take back.</div>
<</if>>

<<timedprogressbar $timer>>
  <<goto "P03">>
<</timedprogressbar>>

[[Nod once|P04]]
<<if $stress > 30 or $anger > 15>>[[Hold the stare|P06]]<</if>>
<<if visited("P02") >= 2>>[[Say nothing|P12]]<</if>>


:: P03
<<set $stress += 4>><<set $anger += 3>>
<div class="dialogue">I'll count your breaths out loud. Spine fog tells me how sharp I need to be.</div>
<div class="dialogue">Don't fail the test by trying to pass it. Just be air. I'll do the bleeding.</div>

<<if $stress > 55>>
  <<timedprogressbar $timer>>
    <<goto "P10">>
  <</timedprogressbar>>
<</if>>

<<if $stress <= 95>>[[Admit you're here|P04]]<</if>>
[[Keep your distance|P06]]


:: P04
<<set $stress += 6>>
<div class="dialogue">They handed me a last little box at the door. Polite dismissal, winter label and all.</div>
<div class="dialogue">I carried it like a small coffin and pretended it was just office supplies.</div>

<<timedprogressbar $timer>>
  <<goto "P11">>
<</timedprogressbar>>

