:: P05
<<set $stress += 3>><<set $anger += 6>>
<div class="dialogue">You say her without her name. It still shivers the rafters.</div>
<div class="dialogue">I flinch, then steady—like a fish learning the hook isn't going anywhere.</div>

<<timedprogressbar $timer>>
  <<goto "P11">>
<</timedprogressbar>>

