:: P07
<<set $stress -= 6>>
<div class="dialogue">Plain listening. No ceremony. I'll try to keep the knives out of my tongue.</div>
<div class="dialogue">Stay steady and I'll stop testing the floorboards every time you breathe.</div>
<<if visited("P07") > 1>>
<div class="dialogue">See? Easier to talk when the room isn't grading me.</div>
<</if>>

<<timedprogressbar $timer>>
