:: P08
<<set $stress -= 8>>
<div class="dialogue">I'll meet the morning steady if you count with me. No rescue, just witness.</div>
<div class="dialogue">If I fall, call it landing. Truth doesn't need a cushion.</div>

<<timedprogressbar $timer>>
  <<goto "P11">>
<</timedprogressbar>>

