:: P09
<<set $anger += 70>>
<div class="dialogue">You reach. I misread. I grab. Nails kiss your throat. The attic shuts its only eye.</div>
<div class="dialogue">Wrong night, wrong shadow. The house swallows the echo.</div>

''You have died.''

[[Again|P01]]


:: P10
<<set $stress += 70>>
<div class="dialogue">Silence turns to paste. Your lungs forget the trick. Dust collects the rent.</div>
<div class="dialogue">The room keeps the last coin of breath for itself.</div>

''You have died.''

[[Again|P01]]


:: P11
<div class="dialogue">Resignation paces the beams. I talk faster so it can't build a nest where you stand.</div>
<div class="dialogue">If you leave now, the absence will come back later and roar like thunder.</div>
<<if visited("P11") > 1>>
<div class="dialogue">Still here? Fine. Then let's be exact and keep going.</div>
<</if>>

<<if $stress > 45>>
