:: P12
<div class="dialogue">Either you returned, or I finally dreamed you right. The room remembers something I can't.</div>
<div class="dialogue">Let me risk the truer piece before it ducks behind the beams again.</div>
<<if visited("P12") > 1>>
<div class="dialogue">Second try, then. Maybe the hinge speaks clearer when we listen worse.</div>
<</if>>

<<timedprogressbar $timer>>
  <<goto "P11">>
<</timedprogressbar>>

