<<set $stress -= 10>><<set $anger -= 6>>
<div class="dialogue">Under every thought there's a bruise. Hear it? I can, finally. Don't blink now.</div>
<div class="dialogue">If you can stand in it without flinching, I can say it without shattering.</div>

<<timedprogressbar $timer>>
  <<goto "P11">>
<</timedprogressbar>>

